## Impact on Customers

### Current PSU-3000 Owners

{% callout type="note" %}
**No immediate action required.** Your existing PSU-3000 units will continue to be fully supported:

- **Firmware updates**: Until 2028-06-30 (3 years)
- **Technical support**: Until 2031-06-30 (5 years)
- **Spare parts availability**: Until 2031-06-30 (5 years)
- **Calibration services**: Until 2031-06-30 (5 years)
{% /callout %}

### New Orders

Customers placing new orders should consider:

1. **Before 2026-01-15**: Both PSU-3000 and PSU-3000-X available
   - PSU-3000: Current pricing, immediate availability
   - PSU-3000-X: Premium pricing initially, may have lead time

2. **After 2026-01-15**: Only PSU-3000-X available for new orders
   - Some PSU-3000 inventory may remain (while supplies last)
   - Contact sales for availability

### Existing Purchase Orders

Purchase orders for PSU-3000 series received before the last order date (2026-01-15) will be honored based on:

- **Stock availability**: Units will be fulfilled from existing inventory
- **Lead time**: May be extended as production winds down
- **Substitution option**: Customers may request PSU-3000-X substitution at equivalent pricing

Contact your sales representative to discuss options for existing orders.

